WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:29.260 --> 00:00:43.829
When we say we are seeking, we must know that
we are a special category of people.

00:00:43.829 --> 00:00:47.489
People were seeking before also.

00:00:47.489 --> 00:00:58.230
They were seeking power, money, possessions,
affluence, every sort of thing.

00:00:58.230 --> 00:01:07.240
Still they are not satisfied - those who have
got it.

00:01:07.240 --> 00:01:18.210
And so those who are seeking the truth are
the highest, highest of all in the evolution.

00:01:18.210 --> 00:01:29.500
They are the ones who are going to jump into
that higher state which is called as self-realization.

00:01:29.500 --> 00:01:36.490
If you are not seeking, then nobody can force
seeking on you.

00:01:36.490 --> 00:01:39.780
It cannot be done.

00:01:39.780 --> 00:01:48.940
Even by force, if you take somebody to the
beautiful lake of nectar of God's love and

00:01:48.940 --> 00:01:56.000
even if you force the person to drink it,
it is you who has to enjoy it and unless and

00:01:56.000 --> 00:01:59.913
until you have the seeking, you will not have
the sensitivity to enjoy that nectar.

00:01:59.913 --> 00:02:06.190
And truth is what it is.

00:02:06.190 --> 00:02:13.500
We cannot change it, we cannot organize it,
we cannot transform it.

00:02:13.500 --> 00:02:19.000
It is, it has been, it will be.

00:02:19.000 --> 00:02:20.890
And what is the truth?

00:02:20.890 --> 00:02:33.900
The truth is that God loves us, that His divine
power of love is all-pervading, is everywhere,

00:02:33.900 --> 00:02:42.139
that this power is acting all the time - it
is a living power of a living God - and that

00:02:42.139 --> 00:02:48.489
this power does all the things that we call
as living work of God.

00:02:48.489 --> 00:02:53.700
A flower is transformed into a fruit by this
power.

00:02:53.700 --> 00:02:56.739
This body we get out of that power.

00:02:56.739 --> 00:03:00.430
From amoeba to this stage we have come out
of that power.

00:03:00.430 --> 00:03:03.409
The whole world is created out of that power.

00:03:03.409 --> 00:03:12.180
In everything that power resides and works
out, sorts out, co-ordinates things for us.

00:03:12.180 --> 00:03:14.959
Above all, it is the love of God.

00:03:14.959 --> 00:03:17.129
It's the compassion of God.

00:03:17.129 --> 00:03:28.010
We human beings have not got the comprehension
of His love; we try to see Him through our

00:03:28.010 --> 00:03:34.139
own angles, through our short sight, through
our blinkers that we have got.

00:03:34.139 --> 00:03:37.730
He is the ocean, ocean of love.

00:03:37.730 --> 00:03:44.169
All the oceans put together cannot be compared
with that ocean of love, that ocean of forgiveness,

00:03:44.169 --> 00:03:48.549
an ocean of complete well-being for us.

00:03:48.549 --> 00:03:53.279
Only thing, we have to jump into it.

00:03:53.279 --> 00:03:58.400
We have to enter into His kingdom.

00:03:58.400 --> 00:04:01.909
That is what one has to do.

00:04:01.909 --> 00:04:05.409
When it is accomplished, then you are just
there.

00:04:05.409 --> 00:04:08.450
You are looked after.

00:04:08.450 --> 00:04:15.779
That is the domain of God I am talking about
and there, when you enter in, as a by-product,

00:04:15.779 --> 00:04:23.170
all kinds of well-being are blessed upon you,
just they are bestowed upon you.

00:04:23.170 --> 00:04:26.320
You just get them automatically.

00:04:26.320 --> 00:04:31.340
But this happening also is not our doing.

00:04:31.340 --> 00:04:34.280
This also is the doing of God.

00:04:34.280 --> 00:04:41.199
He has arranged us in this way that you can
see in the chart - this is the life tree - or

00:04:41.199 --> 00:04:44.460
you (can) say the tree of life as described.

00:04:44.460 --> 00:04:47.160
And this is the one that is within us already
placed.

00:04:47.160 --> 00:04:59.040
All these centers, which are subtle centers,
are expressed outside as gross centers.

00:04:59.040 --> 00:05:05.600
When this residual force of Kundalini, which
people must have explained to you, from that

00:05:05.600 --> 00:05:12.840
sacred bone or sacrum rises and pierces through
all these centers, it enlightens all of them

00:05:12.840 --> 00:05:14.190
one by one.

00:05:14.190 --> 00:05:21.590
By that enlightenment only, you get your physical
well-being, your mental well-being, your emotional

00:05:21.590 --> 00:05:25.420
well-being and ultimately, your spiritual
well being.

00:05:25.420 --> 00:05:27.820
That means you become the spirit.

00:05:27.820 --> 00:05:33.660
Once you become that absolute, the absolute,
then all relativity drops off.

00:05:33.660 --> 00:05:38.730
We actually live in a relative world which
is false, which is not true.

00:05:38.730 --> 00:05:43.840
This power has its own telecommunication.

00:05:43.840 --> 00:05:49.500
It's so tremendous that it is unbelievable
that such a power exists around us and we

00:05:49.500 --> 00:05:51.350
are not aware of it.

00:05:51.350 --> 00:05:53.110
We are not aware of many things.

00:05:53.110 --> 00:05:57.250
We are not aware that this Mother Earth is
moving with such a tremendous speed.

00:05:57.250 --> 00:06:00.440
We are standing on top of that; nothing happens
to you.

00:06:00.440 --> 00:06:02.690
We are not aware of the gravity.

00:06:02.690 --> 00:06:10.740
We are not aware of many things because God
is so kind, so gentle and so thoughtful that

00:06:10.740 --> 00:06:14.110
He wants us to live happily as human beings.

00:06:14.110 --> 00:06:23.110
So He doesn't want us to hear some things
which are not good for us, for our ears, so

00:06:23.110 --> 00:06:27.670
He makes the frequency of these things so
sharp that we can't hear with these ears.

00:06:27.670 --> 00:06:33.150
Some of them, He makes them so low that you
can't hear.

00:06:33.150 --> 00:06:36.080
Only what you can hear and enjoy He makes
you hear.

00:06:36.080 --> 00:06:43.150
But we in our freedom have done a lot of wrong
to ourselves, to each other, to our society,

00:06:43.150 --> 00:06:45.430
to the whole world.

00:06:45.430 --> 00:06:57.360
Once we realize, this freedom is nothing but
is our ego, our ego, which has created this

00:06:57.360 --> 00:07:01.060
problem for all other people.

00:07:01.060 --> 00:07:06.790
Then we have also another thing where we get
conditioned, which creates the superego.

00:07:06.790 --> 00:07:12.010
Now in our activity, which is the right side
sympathetic nervous system, we accumulate

00:07:12.010 --> 00:07:18.700
this horrible thing called ego, because when
we act, we think we are doing it, we are in-charge.

00:07:18.700 --> 00:07:20.400
We are not.

00:07:20.400 --> 00:07:22.660
He is in charge.

00:07:22.660 --> 00:07:25.480
We are really doing nothing.

00:07:25.480 --> 00:07:27.750
What are we doing?

00:07:27.750 --> 00:07:34.650
Like the people ask me, "Mother how can you
cure everything so easily?"

00:07:34.650 --> 00:07:36.020
It's simple.

00:07:36.020 --> 00:07:37.402
How do you make a flower into a fruit?

00:07:37.402 --> 00:07:38.950
To us, we take it for granted.

00:07:38.950 --> 00:07:42.500
We are not bothered to find out, but can you
do it?

00:07:42.500 --> 00:07:43.520
It's so difficult.

00:07:43.520 --> 00:07:45.430
Can you do it?

00:07:45.430 --> 00:07:47.930
We can't.

00:07:47.930 --> 00:07:50.830
But if it is God's power, it can do it.

00:07:50.830 --> 00:07:56.040
So if you also have the God's power flowing
in you, which will happen to you as soon as

00:07:56.040 --> 00:07:59.940
you get your realization, you can do it; anybody
can do it.

00:07:59.940 --> 00:08:01.009
It's very simple.

00:08:01.009 --> 00:08:06.280
Like any instrument, when it is put to the
mains, it starts acting and then we can see

00:08:06.280 --> 00:08:08.510
that it is an instrument.

00:08:08.510 --> 00:08:12.580
Otherwise it looks like some funny stuff here.

00:08:12.580 --> 00:08:13.890
It has to be put to the mains.

00:08:13.890 --> 00:08:19.330
The instrument is ready, but within us these
two things, called the ego and superego as

00:08:19.330 --> 00:08:25.810
a result of our activity and as a result of
our conditioning, are accumulated in our brain.

00:08:25.810 --> 00:08:29.400
These two are to be sucked in.

00:08:29.400 --> 00:08:37.289
That's very important because when they grow,
these two elements - or two, we can, say balloon-like

00:08:37.289 --> 00:08:49.230
structures - they make a very strong gap filled
with calcium and you become an egg.

00:08:49.230 --> 00:08:50.230
Another becomes an egg.

00:08:50.230 --> 00:08:51.889
Third person becomes an egg.

00:08:51.889 --> 00:08:57.760
You develop your I-ness - I am this, I am
that.

00:08:57.760 --> 00:09:04.020
All kinds of misidentifications start coming
on us.

00:09:04.020 --> 00:09:08.930
When this is to be sucked, what should we
do?

00:09:08.930 --> 00:09:11.380
That's the question.

00:09:11.380 --> 00:09:12.640
What are we to do?

00:09:12.640 --> 00:09:14.820
To raise the Kundalini.

00:09:14.820 --> 00:09:20.170
As I said, it is a living process and you
cannot do any living work - so just can't

00:09:20.170 --> 00:09:21.170
do it.

00:09:21.170 --> 00:09:22.170
It is as simple as that.

00:09:22.170 --> 00:09:25.600
You yourself can't do it.

00:09:25.600 --> 00:09:32.110
But somebody who is enlightened, who is the
light, can enlighten another light, because

00:09:32.110 --> 00:09:37.980
that light is ready, just ready, but you need
an enlightened light to enlighten that light.

00:09:37.980 --> 00:09:41.590
Once that light is enlightened, that light
can enlighten another light.

00:09:41.590 --> 00:09:46.480
But the problem is when the light which is
enlightened tries to say that "You are to

00:09:46.480 --> 00:09:48.560
be enlightened," immediately you hit that
person.

00:09:48.560 --> 00:09:52.940
You don't like it because ego is there, which
is ignorance.

00:09:52.940 --> 00:09:55.750
That's how people like Christ were crucified.

00:09:55.750 --> 00:10:00.310
What wrong did He do to people except that,
see, He said, "I am the light?"

00:10:00.310 --> 00:10:01.310
It's true.

00:10:01.310 --> 00:10:02.310
He was the light.

00:10:02.310 --> 00:10:04.020
No doubt that He was the son of God.

00:10:04.020 --> 00:10:09.270
It's true, He was the son of God which you
can prove - on vibrations.

00:10:09.270 --> 00:10:13.030
By this Sahaja Yoga, you can prove it what
He was.

00:10:13.030 --> 00:10:16.470
He was that, but that time people killed Him.

00:10:16.470 --> 00:10:17.470
Why?

00:10:17.470 --> 00:10:21.400
Only because He said, "I am the light," and
