00:10:42.480 --> 00:10:44.760
What has been accomplished?

00:10:44.760 --> 00:10:46.730
Nobody thinks about it - what has been accomplished.

00:10:46.730 --> 00:10:53.490
So we have to take reference from other people,
those who have been deeper than us, who have

00:10:53.490 --> 00:10:57.389
gone into it, who have found out certain things
about Christ.

00:10:57.389 --> 00:11:03.510
And they say that Christ accomplished the
greatest thing, the greatest feat, because

00:11:03.510 --> 00:11:05.900
He was nothing but Omkara.

00:11:05.900 --> 00:11:09.810
He was nothing but the vibrations.

00:11:09.810 --> 00:11:14.050
That's why He had no body and only He could
accomplish it.

00:11:14.050 --> 00:11:15.050
And what did He do?

00:11:15.050 --> 00:11:22.090
Is to accomplish Himself on this cross where
we have this ego and superego.

00:11:22.090 --> 00:11:23.740
Of course they say that He said he died for
our sins.

00:11:23.740 --> 00:11:24.740
How did He die for our sins?

00:11:24.740 --> 00:11:29.290
We say that He died for our sins.

00:11:29.290 --> 00:11:34.230
We accept it, yes, because Churches are telling,
people are telling, Bible is telling.

00:11:34.230 --> 00:11:35.490
