00:12:14.050 --> 00:12:15.050
How do you believe?

00:12:15.050 --> 00:12:16.050
Why are you so self-opinionated?

00:12:16.050 --> 00:12:20.890
If you are born again, what happens to you?

00:12:20.890 --> 00:12:21.890
What happens to you?

00:12:21.890 --> 00:12:23.790
What is born again in you?"

00:12:23.790 --> 00:12:30.890
Born again is nothing but the Kundalini awakening,
which rises on top of your head and here is

00:12:30.890 --> 00:12:33.420
the seat of your Spirit.

00:12:33.420 --> 00:12:38.470
Of course, it resides in your heart, but the
