00:12:38.470 --> 00:12:43.770
that seat, immediately you start feeling that
subtle thing which is all-pervading within

00:12:43.770 --> 00:12:44.770
you.

00:12:44.770 --> 00:12:47.089
For the first time you feel this cool breeze
of the Holy Ghost.

00:12:47.089 --> 00:12:55.350
Holy Ghost is nothing but the power of God,
the power of His love, which is called as

00:12:55.350 --> 00:12:57.910
Adi Shakti in Sanskrit language.

00:12:57.910 --> 00:13:03.930
We don't have to accept anything else from
outside, any dictionary we don't have to accept

00:13:03.930 --> 00:13:09.899
to give answers to things, to mysteries that
we have been suffering all these days.

00:13:09.899 --> 00:13:21.990
Once this cross, which is between the ego
and superego is enlightened, Christ is awakened

00:13:21.990 --> 00:13:22.990
there.

