01:04:29.650 --> 01:04:35.050
First when the Kundalini rises - all right?

01:04:35.050 --> 01:04:39.240
- you won't feel anything, most of you won't
feel anything, but some of you may feel.

01:04:39.240 --> 01:04:42.380
