01:04:42.380 --> 01:04:48.510
You may feel kind of a, some people might
feel the throbbing in the back in the spinal

01:04:48.510 --> 01:04:51.299
cord, might feel, little, not much.

01:04:51.299 --> 01:04:53.670
It's not very painful or anything.

01:04:53.670 --> 01:04:54.780
Don't be frightened of anything.

01:04:54.780 --> 01:04:56.980
Then it will rise.

01:04:56.980 --> 01:05:01.109
Some of you might feel the rising, because
if there are obstructions you can feel the

01:05:01.109 --> 01:05:02.109
rising.

01:05:02.109 --> 01:05:05.839
If there isn't any obstruction, if you are
not misidentified, if you are not extremist,

01:05:05.839 --> 01:05:10.710
if you are in the center, normally it shoots
off in the split of a second.

01:05:10.710 --> 01:05:16.420
When it shoots off, what do you feel is, you
feel a cool breeze coming out of your head.

01:05:16.420 --> 01:05:20.809
But normally, as I have seen, people are complicated.

01:05:20.809 --> 01:05:23.770
There are complications in the physical, mental
or emotional being.

01:05:23.770 --> 01:05:25.330
People are not so balanced.

01:05:25.330 --> 01:05:28.490
Mostly they have liver problems or such things
like that.

01:05:28.490 --> 01:05:30.970
You might get heat coming out.

01:05:30.970 --> 01:05:33.960
First the heat comes; quite a lot of heat
might come.

01:05:33.960 --> 01:05:38.810
When the heat disappears, then you start feeling
the cool coming and you feel very nice inside.

01:05:38.810 --> 01:05:40.930
Then the bliss starts coming.

01:05:40.930 --> 01:05:46.410
You start feeling absolutely relaxed and you
feel in your hands the cool breeze is coming.

01:05:46.410 --> 01:05:48.470
But first of all you feel on the head.

01:05:48.470 --> 01:05:50.349
You should feel yourself.

01:05:50.349 --> 01:05:51.869
Nobody is going to certify it for you.

01:05:51.869 --> 01:05:53.280
There is no falsehood about it.

01:05:53.280 --> 01:05:56.310
It's a thing that you have to feel it.

01:05:56.310 --> 01:06:01.920
And once it happens to you then you can develop
it.

01:06:01.920 --> 01:06:07.799
Because though the Kundalini at the first
shot comes out but then She tries to look

01:06:07.799 --> 01:06:14.319
after your different organs if they are sick,
your mind if it is overloaded, or anything

01:06:14.319 --> 01:06:18.569
that is wrong it creates a balance [unclear
Side B 34:42]...

01:06:18.569 --> 01:06:22.760
So you have to just know how to reestablish
it yourself because it is your own.

01:06:22.760 --> 01:06:23.890
Everything is your own.

01:06:23.890 --> 01:06:27.460
It's - you can think like this that this light
is your own.

01:06:27.460 --> 01:06:29.660
It is your own lamp.

01:06:29.660 --> 01:06:33.680
I just have come because I have got the flame
in Me, perhaps.

01:06:33.680 --> 01:06:35.190
Then I put the lamp.

01:06:35.190 --> 01:06:36.790
Your light is enlightened.

01:06:36.790 --> 01:06:38.650
Now you look after your light.

01:06:38.650 --> 01:06:40.660
It's your light, it's everything yours.

01:06:40.660 --> 01:06:41.860
The power is yours.

01:06:41.860 --> 01:06:42.900
It's your mother.

01:06:42.900 --> 01:06:46.119
It's your own spirit.

01:06:46.119 --> 01:06:48.150
And then you work it out.

01:06:48.150 --> 01:06:56.510
Unless and until you work it out, you will
not know whether it is true or not.

01:06:56.510 --> 01:06:57.809
You have to work it out.

01:06:57.809 --> 01:07:02.250
Now you should not be identified with anything,
that's one thing is true; because you have

01:07:02.250 --> 01:07:03.869
not seen the reality so far.

01:07:03.869 --> 01:07:06.830
Say, for example, Mr X says, "This one says
so."

01:07:06.830 --> 01:07:10.090
All right, must have said it but he is not
here.

01:07:10.090 --> 01:07:13.330
Today he is not here; it is I who am sitting
here.

01:07:13.330 --> 01:07:14.330
All right?

01:07:14.330 --> 01:07:18.559
So it is better that what I am saying you
better receive it because it's nice to live

01:07:18.559 --> 01:07:19.559
with the past.

01:07:19.559 --> 01:07:24.910
Like, people want to believe in the past because
it is easy to handle the past, or live with

01:07:24.910 --> 01:07:28.320
the future because it is easy, or live with
somebody who has written a book or something

01:07:28.320 --> 01:07:29.670
he had done to us.

01:07:29.670 --> 01:07:35.071
But why not believe in yourself that so far
you have not got anything of your own and

01:07:35.071 --> 01:07:39.069
I am saying that you have to get it of your
own.

01:07:39.069 --> 01:07:43.859
That's the main point I am trying to say,
that you must not believe into anything till

01:07:43.859 --> 01:07:46.130
you have found it yourself within your self.

01:07:46.130 --> 01:07:47.380
That's what it is.

01:07:47.380 --> 01:07:51.990
And if you are identified with other things
which you have been doing - most of the people

01:07:51.990 --> 01:07:55.810
who have paid to some Guru or some thing,
get very much identified with them.

01:07:55.810 --> 01:07:57.240
But what have they given you?

01:07:57.240 --> 01:07:58.619
Have they given you any powers?

01:07:58.619 --> 01:07:59.619
Nothing.

01:07:59.619 --> 01:08:00.619
Can you feel another person?

01:08:00.619 --> 01:08:04.829
In collective consciousness, you should be
able to feel another person.

01:08:04.829 --> 01:08:09.490
After realization, immediately you can start
feeling another person and yourself.

01:08:09.490 --> 01:08:15.579
Immediately you can feel, but you need sensitivity
which we lack quite a lot in the Western world

01:08:15.579 --> 01:08:17.380
because the [unclear sounds like 'light is
very small' Side B 36:36].

01:08:17.380 --> 01:08:21.440
But in India I have seen people get realization
(and) immediately they start feeling it like

01:08:21.440 --> 01:08:22.440
that.

01:08:22.440 --> 01:08:27.470
It's very easy to cure Indians, I must say,
but difficult to cure Western people.

01:08:27.470 --> 01:08:31.400
They are very complicated, ego-oriented, over-read,
all that is there.

01:08:31.400 --> 01:08:36.330
But once the Western get it, they settle down
much faster, much better, much deeply than

01:08:36.330 --> 01:08:37.339
Indians do.

